%h1(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 1.77em;")
  Features Update

%p(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;")
  Hello again,

%p(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;")
  I've been reengineering ScoutActivity to be even more helpful tool for your Unit in providing awesome activities to Scouts. I've applied a number of tweaks that I felt were needed through my own usage of ScoutActivity with my Troop.


%p(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;")
  I've changed the focus to be first on highlighting activity ideas for Units, and I'm now allowing everyone to not only vote on them, but propose their own. Links to the list of all activities, which can be filtered, is now on the home page. We still profile some lists such as these which are pre-filtered for you:

%ul(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;")
  %li= link_to "Troop Activity Ideas", troop_activity_ideas_url(utm_source: 'update-email', utm_medium: 'email', utm_campgaign: 'basic')
  %li= link_to "COVID Safe Troop Activity Ideas", covid_safe_troop_activity_ideas_url(utm_source: 'update-email', utm_medium: 'email', utm_campgaign: 'basic')
  %li= link_to "Fundraising Ideas", fundraising_activity_ideas_url(utm_source: 'update-email', utm_medium: 'email', utm_campgaign: 'basic')

%p(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;")
  The second component of Scoutactivity is creating a list of activities for your own Unit to vote on. You can easily copy, through a copy link on each activity's description page, any of the activities in the lists above, or any activity in any Unit on ScoutActivity. Just copy, and then you can edit to tailor it for your own Unit. To copy, you need to be logged in, and you need to be either the owner or and admin on your Unit.

%div(style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;margin-top:0rem;text-align:center")= image_tag "feature-copy-icon.png", width: '50px'

