  %p(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;")
    Two other useful links for your Unit that you can use to promote others to adding or viewing activies are the following:
    %ul(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;")
      %li= link_to unit_sign_up_url(@unit), unit_sign_up_url(@unit)
      %li= link_to unit_activities_url(@unit), unit_activities_url(@unit)

%p(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;")
  Lastly, join me on the ScoutActivity Facebook page, where you can post any feature requests and see what others are saying. Its a great place to let me know about something you'd like to make ScoutActivity even more useful to you.
  = succeed(".") do
    = link_to "https://www.facebook.com/groups/scoutactivity", "https://www.facebook.com/groups/scoutactivity"



